  <summary date="2022-10-15T15:02:09Z" status="Introduced in House">Marginal Well Protection Act

This bill prohibits the Environmental Protection Agency from imposing fees for methane emissions from wells that produce less than 15 barrels of oil per day and less than 90 Mcf (90,000 cubic feet) of natural gas per day.</summary>
